"title": "7150: righteous, the",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7150: righteous, the",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The designation, especially in the OT, of those who live and act in accordance with God's commands.</p>\n<h2>Characteristics of the righteous</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:7\">PRO 20:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:21\">PSA 37:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:11\">PRO 10:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:20-Prov10:21\">PRO 10:20–10:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:31-Prov10:32\">PRO 10:31–10:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:5\">PRO 12:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:5\">PRO 13:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:28\">PRO 15:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:25-Prov21:26\">PRO 21:25–21:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:7\">PRO 29:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:27\">PRO 29:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:31-Matt25:40\">MAT 25:31–25:40</a></p>\n<h2>God's dealings with the righteous</h2>\n<h3>He loves them</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:8\">PSA 146:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:20-Gen18:32\">GEN 18:20–18:32</a></p>\n<h3>He protects them</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:10\">PRO 18:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:5-Ps1:6\">PSA 1:5–1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:16-Ps37:17\">PSA 37:16–37:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:39\">PSA 37:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:22\">PSA 55:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:29\">PRO 10:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:8\">PRO 11:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:21\">PRO 12:21</a></p>\n<h3>He provides for them</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:3\">PRO 10:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:25\">PSA 37:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:25\">PRO 13:25</a></p>\n<h3>He blesses them</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:12\">PSA 5:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:7\">JOB 36:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:33\">PRO 3:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:6-Prov10:7\">PRO 10:6–10:7</a></p>\n<h3>He hears their petitions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:12\">1PE 3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:17\">PSA 34:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:29\">PRO 15:29</a></p>\n<h2>The faith of the righteous</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:4\">HAB 2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:17\">ROM 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:11\">GAL 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:38\">HEB 10:38</a></p>\n<h2>The righteous are secure</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:3\">PRO 12:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:30\">PRO 10:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:28\">PRO 11:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:7\">PRO 12:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:1\">PRO 28:1</a></p>\n<h2>The righteous can be corrupted</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:24\">EZK 18:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:8\">EXO 23:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:19\">DEU 16:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps125:3\">PSA 125:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:20\">EZK 3:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:12-Ezek33:13\">EZK 33:12–33:13</a></p>\n<h2>The oppression of the righteous</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:12-Ps37:13\">PSA 37:12–37:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:17-Ps31:18\">PSA 31:17–31:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:21\">PSA 94:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:11-Lam4:13\">LAM 4:11–4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:6-Amos2:7\">AMO 2:6–2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:12\">AMO 5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:4\">HAB 1:4</a></p>\n<h2>The equality, in human terms, of the righteous and the wicked</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:45\">MAT 5:45</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:12-Eccl8:14\">ECC 8:12–8:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:1-Eccl9:2\">ECC 9:1–9:2</a></p>\n<h2>The reward of the righteous</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:16\">PRO 10:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:29\">PSA 37:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps58:10-Ps58:11\">PSA 58:10–58:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:12-Ps92:15\">PSA 92:12–92:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:6-Prov10:7\">PRO 10:6–10:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:28\">PRO 10:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:23\">PRO 11:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:30-Prov11:31\">PRO 11:30–11:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:21-Prov13:22\">PRO 13:21–13:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:6\">PRO 15:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:10\">ISA 3:10</a></p>\n<h2>The death of the righteous</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:1\">ISA 57:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:15\">PSA 116:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:32\">PRO 14:32</a></p>\n<h2>The hope of the righteous</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:12-Luke14:14\">LUK 14:12–14:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:14-Ps17:15\">PSA 17:14–17:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:32\">PRO 14:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:17-Mal3:18\">MAL 3:17–3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:14-Acts24:16\">ACT 24:14–24:16</a></p>",
